Package Summary
Package Description
com.model
Here are all the models to store the data needed for the game.
com.view
This package contains every element used to display things.
com.view.component
This package contains all the components that are used in a panel, see com.view.panel.
com.view.panel
This package contains all the panels that are used in the MainView.
controller
Here are the classes to make the link between the classes in com.model and com.view
